<h2 id="dataset-1">Dataset</h2>

<h2 id="publication-1">Publication</h2>
<p>Renard, J., Martínez-Almonacid, I., Sonntag, A., Molina, I., Moya-Cuevas, J., Bissoli, G., Muñoz-Bertomeu, J., Faus, I., Niñoles, R., Shigeto, J., Tsutsumi, Y., Gadea, J., Serrano, R., &amp; Bueso, E. (2020). PRX2 and PRX25, peroxidases regulated by COG1, are involved in seed longevity in Arabidopsis. Plant, cell &amp; environment, 43(2), 315–326. https://doi.org/10.1111/pce.13656
