<h2 id="tasks">Tasks</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Rephrase the scientific question (0.5 point).</li>
  <li>Compute the tables of differential expressed genes for both comparisons. Create a histogram of corrected p-values for each comparison (QC). Annotate the genes with their gene symbols and annotation using biomartr (2 points).</li>
  <li>Create a volcano plot for each comparison to display the differential genes. Justify your choice for the fold change cutoff based on the distribution of your log2 fold change values (e.g. median, 75th percentile, etc).</li>
</ol>

